high_descs: Walk toward the stove, then face right counter
Pick up the kettle on the counter
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the kettle in the sink and rinse it
Turn right then face the cabinet on the left of the oven
Open the cabinet then put in the kettle and close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the clean kettle in the cabinet

high_descs: walk to face counter to right of stove
pick up kettle from counter top
wash kettle in sink, remove kettle from sink
walk to face cabinet to the left of the stove
put kettle in bottom cabinet left of the stove
anns.task_desc: put a washed kettle in a cabinet

high_descs: Turn right from the stove to face the counter with a tea kettle
Pick up the kettle from the counter
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the kettle in the sink, run the water, stop the water, and pick the kettle up
Turn around to face the stove
Open the cabinet to the left of the stove and put the kettle inside it
anns.task_desc: Put the clean kettle inside a cabinet
